<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
		<title>Features | Access Granted</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<%- include("../partials/header") %>
		<main class="container">
			<div class="page-content">
				<h1 class="center-text">Features</h1>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Private Posting:</strong> View authorship only if you're a verified member.</li>
					<li><strong>Membership Passcode:</strong> Prevent random access by protecting entry with a secret key.</li>
					<li><strong>Admin Controls:</strong> Admin users can moderate messages and remove inappropriate posts.</li>
					<li><strong>Anonymous From Outside:</strong> Viewers who aren’t logged in see posts — but not authors.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</main>
